  "description": "This individual is an undead remnant animated by tenacious necromantic force, its frame reduced to a light skin lattice of bone and dried connective tissue. Yellow eyes burn steadily within deep, hollow sockets, fixed in an unblinking stare that marks a creature beyond mortal need. Gray hair clings in uneven tufts, and the skull bears old fracture-lines that have knit into hard ridges. The body moves with rigid, deliberate economy, a cavern-haunting sentinel defined by silence, patience, and predatory persistence.",
